com.colorful.atom.beans
Class Feed

java.lang.Object
  com.colorful.atom.beans.Feed

public class Feed
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents an Atom 1.0 feed element.

Author:
Bill Brown 
      atomFeed =
          element atom:feed {
          atomCommonAttributes,
          (atomAuthor*
          & atomCategory*
          & atomContributor*
          & atomGenerator?
          & atomIcon?
          & atomId
          & atomLink*
          & atomLogo?
          & atomRights?
          & atomSubtitle?
          & atomTitle
          & atomUpdated
          & extensionElement*),
          atomEntry*
          }
The default ordering of the entries is by date updated date descending.
See Also:
Atom Syndication Format
